twitch_info.title: I Wanna Kill The Kamilia 3 - Stage 4 (No Devas/Boss Rush) Speedrun in 3:50:30
twitch_info.description:
Decent run, some really silly bad sections brought this time up quite a bit (last RZ save, Influka), but quite a few parts went pretty well (3rd RZ save, Emperor screens). Pretty happy with this for a first run.
YouTube Upload: [http://youtu.be/X3VXRdjZarE](http://youtu.be/X3VXRdjZarE)
